<li><a href="http://eur-lex.europa.eu/JOHtml.do?uri=OJ:L:2003:261:SOM:EN:HTML" class="external text" title="http://eur-lex.europa.eu/JOHtml.do?uri=OJ:L:2003:261:SOM:EN:HTML" rel="nofollow">Initial publication of the International Accounting Standards in the Official Journal of the European Union PB L 261 13-10-2003</a></li>
<li><a href="http://europa.eu/scadplus/leg/en/lvb/l26040.htm" class="external text" title="http://europa.eu/scadplus/leg/en/lvb/l26040.htm" rel="nofollow">Directorate Internal Market of the European Union on the implementation of the IAS in the European Union</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ey.com/global/content.nsf/International/Assurance_-_IFRS_-_Overview" class="external text" title="http://www.ey.com/global/content.nsf/International/Assurance_-_IFRS_-_Overview" rel="nofollow">Ernst &amp; Young IFRS</a> with news and downloadable documents</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pwc.com/ifrs" class="external text" title="http://www.pwc.com/ifrs" rel="nofollow">PwC IFRS page</a> with news and downloadable documents</li>
<li><a href="http://www.iasplus.com/dttpubs/pocket2008.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.iasplus.com/dttpubs/pocket2008.pdf" rel="nofollow">Free 2008 IFRS Pocket Guide from IASPlus - Deloitte</a></li>
</ul>
