<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.kpmgifrg.com/index.cfm" class="external text" title="http://www.kpmgifrg.com/index.cfm" rel="nofollow">KPMG IFRS group</a> with news and downloadable documents</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ifrs.com" class="external text" title="http://www.ifrs.com" rel="nofollow">The American Institute of CPAs (AICPA) in partnership with its marketing and technology subsidiary, CPA2Biz, has developed the IFRS.com web site.</a></li>
</ul>
